  "prompt": "Which is best online shopping site in india for bags?",
  "response": "There are several popular online shopping sites in India where you can find a wide variety of bags. The best site for you may depend on factors such as selection, price, shipping, and return policy. Here are some of the top online shopping sites in India for bags:\n\n1. **Amazon India**: Offers a vast selection of bags from numerous brands across various price ranges, with customer reviews to help guide your decision.\n\n2. **Flipkart**: Similar to Amazon, Flipkart provides a wide range of bags, including both Indian and international brands, with frequent deals and discounts.\n\n3. **Myntra**: Known for fashion and lifestyle products, Myntra offers a curated selection of stylish bags from both well-known and niche brands.\n\n4. **Ajio**: Offers a trendy selection of bags, often featuring unique and stylish designs. Ajio frequently provides discounts and has a user-friendly app and website.\n\n5. **Limeroad**: Specializes in fashion and accessories, providing a wide variety of bags that cater to different tastes and budgets.\n\n6. **Tata CLiQ**: Offers a selection of bags from both luxury and affordable brands, with reliable service and a straightforward shopping experience.\n\n7. **KOOVS**: Focuses on trendy and fashionable items, including a selection of unique and stylish bags that appeal to a younger audience.\n\nEach of these sites has its strengths, so it might be a good idea to browse multiple sites to compare selections and prices.",
